<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Boleto {{codigoAcceso}} - {{nombreCooperativa}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        }
        .ticket-header {
            background-color: #2c3e50;
            color: white;
            padding: 25px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }
        .ticket-header::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -8px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 0;
            height: 0;
            border-left: 8px solid transparent;
            border-right: 8px solid transparent;
            border-top: 8px solid #2c3e50;
        }
        .ticket-header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 300;
        }
        .ticket-header .codigo {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-family: monospace;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin: 10px 0;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 30px 20px;
        }
        .passenger-info {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .passenger-name {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .journey-info {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 25px 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        .city {
            text-align: center;
            flex: 1;
        }
        .city-name {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }
        .province {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6c757d;
        }
        .arrow {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #6c757d;
            margin: 0 15px;
        }
        .details-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .detail-card {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            border-left: 3px solid #6c757d;
        }
        .detail-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6c757d;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .detail-value {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .price-section {
            background-color: #2c3e50;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .price-label {
            font-size: 14px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        .price-value {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 300;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 500;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            background-color: #6c757d;
            color: white;
        }
        .instructions {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            color: #2c3e50;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .instructions h4 {
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }
        .qr-placeholder {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border: 2px solid #e9ecef;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6c757d;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #6c757d;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 10px;
                border-radius: 6px;
            }
            .details-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 10px;
            }
            .journey-info {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 10px;
            }
            .arrow {
                transform: rotate(90deg);
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="ticket-header">
            <h1>Boleto de Viaje</h1>
            <div class="codigo">{{codigoAcceso}}</div>
            <div class="status-badge">{{estado}}</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="passenger-info">
                <div class="passenger-name">{{nombreCliente}}</div>
                <div>{{nombreCooperativa}}</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="journey-info">
                <div class="city">
                    <div class="city-name">{{ciudadOrigen}}</div>
                    <div class="province">{{provinciaOrigen}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="arrow">→</div>
                <div class="city">
                    <div class="city-name">{{ciudadDestino}}</div>
                    <div class="province">{{provinciaDestino}}</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="details-grid">
                <div class="detail-card">
                    <div class="detail-label">Fecha de Viaje</div>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{fechaViaje}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-card">
                    <div class="detail-label">Hora de Salida</div>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{horaSalida}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-card">
                    <div class="detail-label">Asiento</div>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{numeroAsiento}} ({{tipoAsiento}})</div>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-card">
                    <div class="detail-label">Autobús</div>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{numeroAutobus}} - {{placaAutobus}}</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="price-section">
                <div class="price-label">Precio del Boleto</div>
                <div class="price-value">${{precio}}</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="qr-placeholder">
                <div>
                    Código QR<br>
                    {{codigoAcceso}}
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="instructions">
                <h4>Instrucciones Importantes:</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Presenta este boleto (digital o impreso) al abordar</li>
                    <li>Llega 30 minutos antes de la hora de salida</li>
                    <li>Porta tu documento de identidad original</li>
                    <li>El asiento asignado es obligatorio</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>{{nombreCooperativa}}</strong></p>
            <p>¡Buen viaje!</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 